{"type":null,"faqId":38966,"title":"如何查看手环电量？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\r\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p3{margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p4{margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p5{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.875in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p6{margin-left:0.19722222in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.11111111in;}\r\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.31944445in;}\r\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4027778in;}\r\n.s4{font-weight:bold;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span>查看电量有2种方式：</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">1. </span><span>通过APP查看。</span> </p>\n<p><span>手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接时，您可以在APP的设置界面中查看手环电量（可以显示电量百分比）。</span> </p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><img style=\"WIDTH: 1.968in; HEIGHT: 3.363in; VERTICAL-ALIGN: text-bottom\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=126640\"></p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">2. </span><span>通过手环屏幕查看。</span> </p>\n<p class=\"p5\"><span class=\"s2\"> </span><span>手环显示默认主界面时，请点亮屏幕查看电量。</span> </p>\n<p class=\"p6\"><img style=\"WIDTH: 1.495in; HEIGHT: 2.801in; VERTICAL-ALIGN: text-bottom\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=126641\"></p>\n<p><span class=\"s3\"> </span><span>手环切换界面后，请向右滑动屏幕查看电量。</span> </p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><img style=\"WIDTH: 4.149in; HEIGHT: 2.754in; VERTICAL-ALIGN: text-bottom\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=126642\"></p>\n<p><span class=\"s4\">说明：</span><span>手环屏幕上通常不显示数字百分比（仅在充电时显示百分比），只有电量大概的显示。如果想查看详细的电量，建议您通过APP查看。</span> </p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4276","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673016000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":34,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀手环zero、b0-honor、b0、zero、充电、查看电量","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}